00:46:59.130 --> 00:47:01.170
I said, “What makes you think like that?”

00:47:01.170 --> 00:47:05.609
“Because I can see such a big ego on my
head, this could be only Napoleon and I know

00:47:05.609 --> 00:47:06.609
how to draw.

